org.bytedeco.javacv

Class LeptonicaFrameConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacv.FrameConverter<PIX>
      • org.bytedeco.javacv.LeptonicaFrameConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class LeptonicaFrameConverter
extends FrameConverter<PIX>
    A utility class to map data between Frame and PIX, which is the image data structure used by Tesseract. Currently supports only plain PIX images, not FPIX or DPIX ones.
    Author:
    Samuel Audet
